Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-60,0:00:-03.-02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-03.00,0:00:00.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-16,0:00:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.01,0:00:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.37,0:00:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.71,0:00:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.36,0:01:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that sure was an interesting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I've had enough of that ship graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.51,0:01:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not like I wanna live there,\Nbut I wanna visit from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Was it really that nice?\N--Hm? Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's... not rain...\N--Hail?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.46,0:01:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... something's fall--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Caught Log! The King of Salvagers, Masira!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!! Hold on to the ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What is it?! What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream! Yeah, this must be a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dream?! Goo--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! More stuff's falling! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the rudder! The rudder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way that'll work in these waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, protect the ship!\NIt can't take this any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! Hm? Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:03:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cast aside your worries.\NCalmly close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.52,0:03:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you open your eyes,\Na quiet morning lies before you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bones!!\N--You idiot! Don't throw it this way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--More stuff's falling!!\N--Bones!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't throw it this way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did a ship fall from the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, the Grand Line is a crazy place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we see a ship graveyard\Ninside a rainbow mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and then a ship falls from the sky!\N--Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do?! Our Log Pose is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's stuck pointing upwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.93,0:03:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it. It was updated by\Nan island with stronger magnetism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--If the Log Pose needle is pointing upwards,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that means the log has\Nbeen caught by the sky island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A floating island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Did that ship and those\Nbones fall from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.58,0:04:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see anything\Nlike an island in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.25,0:04:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, a sea is what's floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting more and more confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaay! There's a sea with an\Nisland floating in the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's head there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Turn the rudder upwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upwards rudder full!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.28,0:04:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, you can't turn upwards, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I've never seen the\Nsky island, nor do I know much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's impossible for an\Nisland or a sea to float in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Log Pose really must be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Navigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our concern right now should not be the\NLog Pose, it should be how we get to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what weird situations\Nthis ship gets caught up in,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or how panicked we get,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must not doubt the Log Pose.\NThis is an ironclad rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we should doubt is rather\Nthe common sense in our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's definitely an\Nisland where it's pointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that woman doing,\Nopening the coffin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can you learn something from that?\N--I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got strange interests!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pretty woman and the dead,\Nnow that's an interesting combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Jump, Luffy!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exploration, they said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, restoration complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The holes here are man-made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... then this guy was\Npierced there and died, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, these are indications of medical treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's craterization, isn't it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in the past, they made holes in the\Nskull in order to constrain a brain tumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's a medical\Ntechnique from very long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's been at least\N200 years since he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was in his early 30s.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He fell sick while traveling\Non the sea and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason his teeth remained in good\Ncondition compared to his other bones is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because tar was rubbed onto them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.74,0:06:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This custom is characteristic of\Nsome areas in the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So considering history, that was a ship\Nfor an exploration party from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is. The "St. Briss" of Briss,\Na kingdom in the South Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It set sail 208 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same ship as the one that fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nit had a symbol like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship probably wandered in\Nthe sky for at least 200 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find out all that\Njust by looking at bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.41,0:07:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead people may not speak,\Nbut they do hold information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the ship was for an exploration party,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it should still hold various\Nrecords and evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but the ship sank in the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What're you guys doing?!\N--Luffy! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found something incredible! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map of the sky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Skypiea...\N--See? See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean that there's\Nreally an island in the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! The sky island exists!\NIt's a dream island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to a dream island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream island!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so carried away!\NThis only means it might be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're tons of fake maps out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... Sorry! It exists! I'm sure it exists, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Listen, Luffy! I'm telling you,\N--Uhm, Nami, please treat\Nthe ship with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--we don't know how to get there!\N--Uhm, Nami, please treat\Nthe ship with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're the navigator! Figure something out!\N--Uhm, Nami, please treat\Nthe ship with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--There are some things you can't\Njust "figure out," you know!\N--Nami-san's cute when she's angry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't care! We're going to the sky!!\N--Nami-san's cute when she's angry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we can't move\Nthe ship forward this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.85,0:08:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What we need now is\Ninformation, as Robin said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a huge ship like that really went to the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's definitely a way\Nfor this ship to go there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's somehow pull out whatever\Nrecords remain in that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ship has completely sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it sank, then we'll salvage it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright!\N--As if we could!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.31,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's salvage?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means to pull up a sunken ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't work, since that ship is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... You really\Nmake us do reckless things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! I'll be sure to find a clue to the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not, there are no defects in my design.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I wish you... good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chopper. Everyone, please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Luffy. There're tons\Nof monsters down here, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a giant sea snakes' nest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sanji. Whoa! They looked this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.27,0:09:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay.\N--Okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll survive. Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper, hold the brake tight, okay?\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... I'm glad I didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Salvage, salvage!\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salvage, salvage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Salvage, salvage!\N--What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.00,0:10:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salvage, salvage!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Salvage, salvage!\N--Company, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Salvage...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the area where a ship sank?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir! Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By boss... they mean me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to salvage the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sunken ship belongs to me,\Nthe king of salvagers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:11:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the boss of the Masira Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy... weirdoes at a time like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.01,0:11:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! What're you guys\Ndoing there?! This is my turf!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Every ship that sinks\Nin this territory belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't touched anything\Nthat's mine, have you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like... he's going to salvage the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what? Doesn't this work for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit mumbling! Answer my question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.07,0:11:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Can I ask you a question?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me a question?!\NThat's fine. Ask me anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you're going to\Nsalvage the ship. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Do you find me that "monkeyful"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Monkeyful?\N--That means "handsome." Do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:12:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah!\N--Oh, come on, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there isn't such a word, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you gonna salvage it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! If there's a\Nsunken ship in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll salvage it! I'm that kind of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's on the water, I'll sink it and\Nsalvage it! I'm that kind of a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no ship that we can't salvage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... is it okay if we watch you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh, I see, is salvaging work new to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, go ahead and observe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's see how things\Ngo for now, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be... Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss! There's trouble!\N--What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The members who went into\Nthe sea to set the cradle are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they get hurt by Sea Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... it looks like they\Nwere beaten up by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Are you saying there's\Nsomeone down there in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Those idiots...!\N--This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.45,0:13:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone in the sea! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Er... O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing he's an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Hurry up and set the cradle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.13,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start salvaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's waving to us... Don't let him\Nnotice the air supply, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys, imagine that they're pumpkins!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get nervous... just because\Npeople are watching, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop the cradle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for the mysterious enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're doing this\Nout of pride or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to give us a show, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:16:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cradle set, confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that monkey?! What's that monkey for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a discerning eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. This is no ordinary prow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch Barco-hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wow! Amazing!\N--It's really amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,40 meters to the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20... 10...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barco-hunter joint... completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then! I'll start blowing air!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he going to breathe into\Nthat and lift the ship up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Air?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship's body has risen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Pull it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.08,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send more air! On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! The crew that's in the water...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.07,0:18:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?! What happened, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:19:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone in the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare they hurt my guys?!\NWho the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're not taking\Npictures or anything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he posed for us to take pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming! Keep on working\Non the salvaging operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.86,0:19:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? We're fine without the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that they pumped in this much air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who is trying to salvage this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.21,0:20:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something might have happened\Nto Nami-san and Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been calling them, but no response!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you, invading my turf?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Am I that monkeyful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're an imitation monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of conversation is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... What can I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.94,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think so? You have a good eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, underneath the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:21:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah... there's something down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You guys came from the East Blue, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.60,0:21:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But really, you look just like a monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.27,0:21:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complimenting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! What is this thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.66,0:22:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! It's a turtle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sea! Of course we'll see turtles!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.35,0:23:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.35,0:23:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A galleon fell, and then a\Nweird monkey shows up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! It's become pitch dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.56,0:23:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Monsters Appear! Don't Mess\Nwith the Whitebeard Pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
